Definition: a disparaging remark
Example: in the 19th century any reference to female sexuality was considered a vile aspersion; it is difficult for a woman to understand a man's sensitivity to any slur on his virility
Synonyms: verb, communication, asperse, slur, disparagement, a, disparaging, remark, in, the, th, century, any, reference, to, female, sexuality, was, considered, vile, it, is, difficult, for, woman, understand, man, s, sensitivity, on, his, virility
Category: noun.communication
